{"data": [{"id": "4743002", "title": "Datadog Poised To Rule 2025's AI Software Picks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/517395625/photo/dog-running-for-frisbee-in-field.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=EYa8eRM7IRx4bwyb6qjHWC5Jl08BwnRP-um6h1bsnLg=\" alt=\"Dog running for frisbee in field.\" data-id=\"517395625\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dougal Waters/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Through most of 2024 I have stayed neutral on data observability company Datadog (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DDOG\" title=\"Datadog, Inc.\">DDOG</a></span>) as the broader software space that it operated in fell out of the prioritization order among enterprise</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743002-datadog-poised-to-rule-2025s-ai-software-picks", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:16:13"}, {"id": "4743012", "title": "How The U.S.-China Trade Dispute Is Redefining Global Trade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"American Chinese windy day flags fly together on flagpole\" data-id=\"515912196\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5760px\" height=\"3840px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cbarnesphotography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/inga-fechner/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inga Fechner</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/james-knightley/\" rel=\"nofollow\">James Knightley </a></em></p> <h2>China\u2019s declining US market share</h2> <p>The global market landscape has undergone significant transformations since the onset of the US-China trade dispute in 2018. The imposition of tariffs and a shift towards protectionism have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/515912196/image_515912196.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743012-how-us-china-trade-dispute-redefining-global-trade", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:09:00"}, {"id": "4741580", "title": "Allied Gold: Where Growth And Value Intersect", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"native 1.05 gram gold nugget from Kenieba District, Mali, Africa\" data-id=\"1638258887\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>All figures are in United States Dollars unless otherwise noted. G/T = grams per tonne (of gold or silver). GEOs = gold-equivalent ounces. SEOs = silver-equivalent ounces. AISC refers to all-in sustaining costs. LOMP = life of mine plan.</p> <h2>Introduction</h2>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1638258887/image_1638258887.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741580-allied-gold-where-growth-and-value-intersect", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:05:00"}, {"id": "4742948", "title": "Matterport's Arbitrage Opportunity, Navigating The CoStar Acquisition Deal (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Caucasian man with Matterport camera and Tablet doing 3d Scan Virtual Tour indoors\" data-id=\"1442692785\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wirestock</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I covered<strong> Matterport </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MTTR\" title=\"Matterport, Inc.\">MTTR</a></span>) stock<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720851-matterport-mttr-stock-cautious-hold-limited-upside-before-acquisition\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720851-matterport-mttr-stock-cautious-hold-limited-upside-before-acquisition\" target=\"_blank\"> roughly five months</a> after the announcement of its acquisition by <strong>CoStar Group</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSGP\" title=\"CoStar Group, Inc.\">CSGP</a>). At the time, the stock was down roughly 10% from the highs Matterport posted following the acquisition</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442692785/image_1442692785.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742948-matterports-arbitrage-opportunity-navigating-the-costar-acquisition-deal", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4742993", "title": "Catalyst Pharmaceuticals: Agamree Is Its Key To A Sustainable Future", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4663334-catalyst-pharmaceuticals-until-the-teva-anda-is-resolved-there-is-risk\">covered</a> Catalyst Pharma (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CPRX\" title=\"Catalyst Pharmaceuticals, Inc.\">CPRX</a></span>) at its weakest moment in early January, so it is not a big surprise that the stock is up 50%. At that time, Catalyst had just announced a minor $150mn secondary offering</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742993-catalyst-pharma-agamree-is-its-key-to-a-sustainable-future", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:40:18"}, {"id": "4742854", "title": "2 Solid Yields From Preferred Stocks For Uncertain Times", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red squirrel fills up its shopping trolley full of hazelnuts.\" data-id=\"1443871198\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">AGD Beukhof/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-authored with Hidden Opportunities</em></p> <p>Winter is here. The air is crisp, and depending on where you live, the first snow may already be blanketing the ground. Nature instinctively prepares for the season; trees shed their leaves, squirrels hoard nuts, and bears</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1443871198/image_1443871198.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742854-2-solid-yields-from-preferred-stocks-for-uncertain-times", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:35:00"}, {"id": "4742820", "title": "Scotiabank: Still Time To Buy This High-Yielding Blue-Chip Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Scotiabank head office in Toronto.\" data-id=\"1342049706\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Scotiabank's head office in Toronto.</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In investing, the only guarantee is that not all investments are going to pan out. That's because, no matter how capable somebody is, this doesn't change the reality that the facts change over time via external forces. Investment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342049706/image_1342049706.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742820-scotiabank-still-time-to-buy-this-high-yielding-blue-chip-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:30:00"}, {"id": "4742222", "title": "First Industrial Realty: A Top Industrial Pick With Solid Upside Potential", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"REIT. Real estate investment trust. Financial Market. Hand pressing button on screen\" data-id=\"1346878080\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4016px\" height=\"1776px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Funtap</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>REITs have faced their fair share of headwinds over the past two years. And recently pulled back from a short rally this past July due to anticipation of the first rate cut that happened this September.</p> <p>However, with uncertainty surrounding</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346878080/image_1346878080.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742222-first-industrial-realty-a-top-industrial-pick-with-solid-upside-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:23:00"}, {"id": "4742998", "title": "U.S. Dollar Is Offered And China's Politburo Promises More Monetary And Fiscal Support", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual image of man using smartphone to view bar graph\" data-id=\"1359134494\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Overview </strong></h2> <p>The dollar is offered. Neither the 227k rise in nonfarm payrolls, nor the above 3% Q4 growth that the Atlanta Fed sees the economy tracking, or the uptick in November CPI expected to be reported on Wednesday has been sufficient</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742998-us-dollar-offered-chinas-politburo-promises-more-monetary-fiscal-support", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:05:00"}, {"id": "4742726", "title": "Strong Economy, Soaring Profits: What 2025 Means For Your Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"100 new US dollar bills on black background\" data-id=\"1502319014\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">alfexe</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>What a year it's been!</p> <p></p> <p>A new group of self-described \u201c<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vXmTWHORhPo\" rel=\"nofollow\">degenerates</a>\u201d are celebrating their YOLO (you only live once) speculative style of gambling, which became popular during the Pandemic lockdowns.</p> <ul> <li>The Degen Dow has been up 22% since January</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502319014/image_1502319014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742726-strong-economy-soaring-profits-what-2025-means-for-your-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 15:00:00"}]}